---
title: Southeast Asian Chicken & Slaw with Roasted Potato Chunks & Toasted Sesame Dressing
description: We're using our Southeast Asian spice blend to give the classic combo of chicken and potatoes some added flair. Complement it with a colourful slaw and toasted sesame dressing that will bring even more excitement to this devilishly delicious dish.
